## File Structure

Every presentation is a **single self-contained HTML file**:

```
my-topic/
└── index.html   ← everything: HTML + CSS + JS inline
```

If working in a multi-deck repo, also update the root `index.html`:
```html
<li><a href="my-topic/">My Topic Title</a></li>
```

