## Slide Content Patterns

### Hero / Title Slide
- Giant display heading, 1–2 words max per line
- Subtitle in a lighter weight or muted color
- Optional: animated accent line, pill label, or background particle effect
- Use `clamp()` for responsive font sizes: `font-size: clamp(3rem, 8vw, 8rem)`

### Section Intro Slide
- Large section number (low-opacity background element)
- Short bold heading
- 1-sentence description

### Content / List Slide
- Heading at top
- 3–5 bullet points with icons (from icon library)
- Stagger animations on list items
- Keep text sparse — slides are not documents

### Quote Slide
- Huge opening quote mark (decorative, low-opacity)
- Large quote text in a display font
- Attribution in small caps / muted color

### Two-Column Slide
- `.split` grid for visual vs. text, or comparison
- Decorative vertical divider (1px accent line)

### Data / Stat Slide
- 1–3 giant numbers with labels
- Animate numbers counting up on slide entry (JS)
- Keep surrounding text minimal

### Closing / Thank-You Slide
- Bold, simple, energetic
- Optionally loop the background animation faster
- Contact info or CTA in a pill or card

