## Icons — Always Use a Library

Pick **one** and stick to it throughout the deck. Do not use emoji or raw SVGs.

| Library | CDN | Usage |
|---|---|---|
| **Font Awesome** | `https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/font-awesome/6.5.1/css/all.min.css` | `<i class="fa-solid fa-rocket"></i>` |
| **Tabler Icons** | `https://unpkg.com/@tabler/icons-webfont@latest/tabler-icons.min.css` | `<i class="ti ti-rocket"></i>` |
| **Lucide** | `https://unpkg.com/lucide@latest` (JS) | `<i data-lucide="rocket"></i>` + `lucide.createIcons()` |

Use icons on list items, stat callouts, section labels, and nav hints.

